-- Loews Adds RG Advisors’s Gendelman as Head of Equity Investments
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2013-01-11T14:36:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-11/loews-adds-rg-advisors-s-gendelman-as-head-of-equity-investments.html
Loews Corp. (L) , the holding company
controlled by New York’s Tisch family, hired Robert Gendelman as
head of equity investments.  Gendelman previously was chief investment officer at RG
Advisors, New York-based Loews said today in a statement
distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zachary Tracer in New York at 
